### üìß **4. SMTP Details (For Email Alerts)**

| Item | Example | Required? |
|------|---------|-----------|
| SMTP Server | `smtp.gmail.com` / `smtp.office365.com` / `mail.yourcompany.com` | ‚úÖ Yes |
| SMTP Port | `587` (TLS) / `465` (SSL) / `25` (no encryption) | ‚úÖ Yes |
| Authentication required? | Yes / No | ‚úÖ Yes |
| SMTP Username | `alerts@yourcompany.com` | ‚úÖ If auth required |
| SMTP Password / App Password | `your-app-password` | ‚úÖ If auth required |
| From Email Address | `monitoring-alerts@yourcompany.com` | ‚úÖ Yes |
| To Email Address(es) | `sysadmin@yourcompany.com`, `team@yourcompany.com` | ‚úÖ Yes |
| TLS enabled? | Yes / No | ‚úÖ Yes |

> ‚ö†Ô∏è **Gmail Note**: If using Gmail, you need an **App Password** (not your regular password). Enable 2FA first, then generate App Password.

