### üåê **6. Network & Firewall**

| Port | Service | Direction | Required? |
|------|---------|-----------|-----------|
| `9090` | Prometheus Web UI | Inbound to monitoring server | ‚úÖ Yes |
| `9093` | Alertmanager Web UI | Inbound to monitoring server | Optional |
| `3000` | Grafana Web UI | Inbound to monitoring server | ‚úÖ Yes |
| `9100` | Node Exporter | Inbound on Linux servers | ‚úÖ Yes |
| `9182` | Windows Exporter | Inbound on Windows servers | ‚úÖ Yes (Phase 2) |

